Description (short paragraph about the p: "Skeuomorph" is a piece about artifacts dipped in paint that are rendered into a piece of paper on a wall. The video is a journey that shows this process in two different frames. The actions of the figure dipping the objects in paint are hard to make out, and another element of imitation is added by having the dual screens at times. the difficulty in discerning what the figure is doing creates an effect of mystery and labor. Overall the piece is one of the relationships between time, work, and rendering.
